    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Hasnep/setup-roc/releases/tag/v0.5.0\">v0.5.0</a> now has three options for the <code>TESTING</code> input, <code>never</code> is the default and will ignore testing versions, <code>always</code> will only get versions marked as testing and <code>auto</code> will try getting a testing version and if it fails, get a non-testing version instead. Thanks for the feedback <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"515757\">@Luke Boswell</span> and let me know if it works now :)</p>",
        "id": 495855708,
